de.thkoeln.cvogt.android.propanim_utilities

Class AnimatedGuiObjectCV.ObjectProperties

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.thkoeln.cvogt.android.propanim_utilities.AnimatedGuiObjectCV.ObjectProperties
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Enclosing class:
    AnimatedGuiObjectCV<T>

    public static class AnimatedGuiObjectCV.ObjectProperties
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Class to store and later to restore member values of an object of class AnimatedGuiObjectCV - mainly those values that pertain to the presentation of the object on the display. Additional values of any meaning can be stored in a HashMap component, i.e. in a kind of bundle (the class Bundle itself cannot be not used here because it is not serializable).
